WEBVTT

00:08:27.372 --> 00:08:32.571
Når jeg ser det skrevet, er det min opgave
at gøre hvad jeg kan for at fjerne det.

00:08:33.370 --> 00:08:35.848
Jeg kunne ikke foreslå
"everyone held her breath"

00:08:35.872 --> 00:08:37.564
eller "everyone held his breath"

00:08:37.588 --> 00:08:40.150
eller "everyone held his or her breath."

00:08:40.174 --> 00:08:42.994
Mit forslag skulle passe ind.

00:08:43.018 --> 00:08:44.374
Jeg spurgte,
via redaktøren,

00:08:44.398 --> 00:08:46.446
om skribenten ville overveje
at ændre det

00:08:46.470 --> 00:08:49.041
til "all in the vicinity held
their breath"

00:08:49.065 --> 00:08:50.907
Fordi det engelske "all"
er pluralis.

00:08:50.931 --> 00:08:52.088
Nej.

00:08:52.112 --> 00:08:55.342
Jeg prøvede igen: "All those present
held their breath?"

00:08:55.366 --> 00:08:57.587
Jeg tænkte, at det lød
svagt juridisk.

00:08:57.611 --> 00:08:58.858
Men redaktøren påpegede,

00:08:58.882 --> 00:09:01.287
at "present" og "presence"
ikke fungerer